Layout of Registration Data Provided by CGAAI/DRPSP/SPPS/MPS Team

a. Data Specification
Must be provided in .CSV format, separated by semicolons ;.

If a field has no information, do not fill in with fictitious data.


b. Data for ACTIVE Employees
| **Field Name**           | **Data Type** | **Description**                                                                                                        |
| ------------------------ | ------------- | -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| CodigoOrgao              | Text          | CNPJ of the agency to which the employee is linked (no dashes or dots).                                                |
| NomeOrgao                | Text          | Name of the agency the employee is linked to.                                                                          |
| MatriculaServidor        | Text          | Employee registration number (no dashes or dots).                                                                      |
| CpfServidor              | Text          | Employee CPF number (no dashes or dots).                                                                               |
| NúmeroPasepServidor      | Text          | Employee PASEP/PIS/NIT ID number (no dashes or dots).                                                                  |
| Sexo                     | Text          | Gender: "M" for male, "F" for female.                                                                                  |
| EstadoCivil              | Numeric       | Marital status code (see Table 01).                                                                                    |
| DataNascimento           | Date          | Birth date in dd/mm/yyyy format.                                                                                       |
| DataIngressoEnte         | Date          | Date of joining the institution (dd/mm/yyyy).                                                                          |
| DataIngressoServPub      | Date          | Date of joining public service (dd/mm/yyyy).                                                                           |
| DataIngressoUltCarreira  | Date          | Date of joining current career (dd/mm/yyyy).                                                                           |
| DataInícioExercicioCargo | Date          | Date of starting in the current position (dd/mm/yyyy).                                                                 |
| Nomecargo                | Text          | Name of the position held.                                                                                             |
| Codigocargo              | Text          | Code of the position (no dashes or dots).                                                                              |
| AbonoPermanencia         | Text          | "Yes" if receiving permanence allowance, "No" otherwise.                                                               |
| EhProfessor              | Text          | "Yes" if teacher in early education, elementary, or secondary education; "No" otherwise.                               |
| EhMembroMinisterioPub    | Text          | "Yes" if a member of the Public Prosecutor’s Office; "No" otherwise.                                                   |
| EhMagistrado             | Text          | "Yes" if a magistrate; "No" otherwise.                                                                                 |
| EhMembroTCU              | Text          | "Yes" if a member of TCU (Federal Court of Accounts); "No" otherwise.                                                  |
| EhAposentadoriaespecial  | Text          | "Yes" if entitled to special retirement; "No" otherwise.                                                               |
| TipoVinculo              | Numeric       | Type of employment bond (see Table 02).                                                                                |
| SituaçãoFuncional        | Numeric       | Functional status (see Table 03).                                                                                      |
| RemuneracaoContribuiçao  | Numeric       | Remuneration subject to contributions, including positions with commission if applicable (decimal separator is a dot). |

c. Data for RETIREES
| **Field Name**            | **Data Type** | **Description**                                                    |
| ------------------------- | ------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| CodigoOrgao               | Text          | CNPJ of the agency the retiree is linked to (no dashes or dots).   |
| NomeOrgao                 | Text          | Name of the agency.                                                |
| MatriculaAposentado       | Text          | Retiree registration number.                                       |
| CpfAposentado             | Text          | Retiree CPF number.                                                |
| NumeroPasep               | Text          | PASEP/PIS/NIT ID number.                                           |
| SexoAposentado            | Text          | Gender: "M" or "F".                                                |
| EstadoCivilAposentado     | Numeric       | Marital status code (Table 01).                                    |
| DataNascimentoAposentado  | Date          | Date of birth (dd/mm/yyyy).                                        |
| DataIniBenef              | Date          | Start date of the benefit (dd/mm/yyyy).                            |
| ValorBenef                | Numeric       | Monthly benefit amount (decimal separator is a dot).               |
| ValidezAposentado         | Text          | Condition: "V" = valid, "I" = invalid.                             |
| DataPrimeiraElegibilidade | Date          | Date when the retiree became eligible for retirement (dd/mm/yyyy). |
| SituaçãoFuncional         | Numeric       | Functional status (Table 03).                                      |


d. Data for BENEFICIARIES (PENSIONERS)
| **Field Name**                       | **Data Type** | **Description**                                                          |
| ------------------------------------ | ------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| CodigoOrgao                          | Text          | CNPJ of the agency.                                                      |
| NomeOrgao                            | Text          | Agency the deceased employee was linked to.                              |
| MatriculaServidorInstituidor         | Text          | Registration number of deceased employee (optional).                     |
| CpfServidorInstituidor               | Text          | CPF of deceased employee (optional).                                     |
| PasepServidorInstituidor             | Text          | PASEP/PIS/NIT of deceased (optional).                                    |
| DataInicioPensao                     | Date          | Pension start date (dd/mm/yyyy).                                         |
| ValorParcelaBenefícioPensao          | Numeric       | Monthly pension amount for the beneficiary (decimal separator is a dot). |
| DuraçãoPensao                        | Text          | "V" for lifetime pension, "T" for temporary pension.                     |
| CpfPensionista                       | Text          | CPF of the beneficiary.                                                  |
| SexoPensionista                      | Text          | Gender: "M" or "F".                                                      |
| EstadoCivilPensionista               | Numeric       | Marital status (Table 03).                                               |
| DataNascimentoPensionista            | Date          | Birth date (dd/mm/yyyy).                                                 |
| ValidezPensionista                   | Text          | "V" = valid, "I" = invalid.                                              |
| TipoDependenciaPensionista           | Numeric       | Type of dependency (Table 04).                                           |
| SituaçãoFuncionalServidorInstituidor | Numeric       | Functional status of the deceased employee (Table 03) (optional).        |


e. Data for DEPENDENTS
| **Field Name**               | **Data Type** | **Description**                                                         |
| ---------------------------- | ------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| CodigoOrgao                  | Text          | CNPJ of the agency.                                                     |
| NomeOrgao                    | Text          | Name of the agency.                                                     |
| MatriculaInstituidor         | Numeric       | Registration number of active or retired employee (optional).           |
| CpfInstituidor               | Numeric       | CPF of active or retired employee (optional).                           |
| PasepInstituidor             | Numeric       | PASEP/PIS/NIT (optional).                                               |
| TipoDependencia              | Numeric       | Type of dependency (Table 04).                                          |
| FinsPrevidenciarios          | Numeric       | Whether the dependency is for social security purposes ("Yes" or "No"). |
| DataInicioDependencia        | Date          | Start date (dd/mm/yyyy).                                                |
| DataPrevistaFimDependencia   | Date          | Expected end date (dd/mm/yyyy).                                         |
| CpfDependente                | Numeric       | CPF of the dependent.                                                   |
| SexoDependente               | Text          | Gender: "M" or "F".                                                     |
| EstadoCivil                  | Numeric       | Marital status (Table 01).                                              |
| DataNascimentoDependente     | Date          | Date of birth (dd/mm/yyyy).                                             |
| InvalidezDependente          | Numeric       | Condition: "V" = valid, "I" = invalid.                                  |
| SituaçãoFuncionalInstituidor | Numeric       | Functional status of the linked employee (Table 03) (optional).         |


Reference Tables
Table 01 - Marital Status
| Code | Description       |
| ---- | ----------------- |
| 1    | Single            |
| 2    | Married           |
| 3    | Widowed           |
| 4    | Legally Separated |
| 5    | Divorced          |
| 6    | Stable Union      |
| 9    | Others            |


Table 02 - Type of Employment Bond
| Code | Description                                            |
| ---- | ------------------------------------------------------ |
| 1    | Employee in Permanent Position                         |
| 2    | Stable Employee (Other Situations)                     |
| 3    | Employee in Temporary Position                         |
| 4    | Employee in Exclusive Commission Position              |
| 5    | Employee in Elected Position                           |
| 6    | Public Employee under CLT (Labor Law)                  |
| 7    | Stable Non-Permanent Employee under Article 19 of ADCT |
| 8    | Military Employee                                      |
| 99   | Others                                                 |


Table 03 - Functional Status
| Code | Description                  |
| ---- | ---------------------------- |
| 1    | Active                       |
| 2    | Dismissed                    |
| 3    | On Paid Leave                |
| 4    | On Unpaid Leave              |
| 5    | Seconded (with cost)         |
| 6    | Seconded (without cost)      |
| 7    | Requisitioned (with cost)    |
| 8    | Requisitioned (without cost) |
| 9    | Fired                        |
| 10   | In Availability              |
| 11   | Deceased                     |
| 12   | Retired                      |
| 13   | In Prison                    |
| 14   | Military – Reform            |
| 15   | Military – Reserve           |
| 99   | Others                       |



Table 04 - Types of Dependency
| Code | Description                                   |
| ---- | --------------------------------------------- |
| 1    | Spouse                                        |
| 2    | Partner                                       |
| 3    | Minor child (not emancipated)                 |
| 4    | Disabled child                                |
| 5    | Parent with economic dependence               |
| 6    | Stepchild (minor, not emancipated, dependent) |
| 7    | Disabled stepchild (dependent)                |
| 8    | Minor sibling (dependent)                     |
| 9    | Disabled sibling (dependent)                  |
| 10   | Ward                                          |
| 11   | Grandchild                                    |
| 12   | Ex-spouse receiving alimony                   |
| 99   | Others                                        |



### From the raw datasets:

| **Variable Name** | **Probable Meaning / Description**                                                 |
| ----------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `id_servidor`     | Unique identifier for the employee (civil servant ID)                              |
| `id_vinculo`      | ID of the employment bond / contract                                               |
| `id_mes`          | ID of the month record                                                             |
| `mes`             | Month (e.g., 202201 for January 2022)                                              |
| `id_funcionario`  | Another unique identifier for the employee (possibly different from `id_servidor`) |
| `nome`            | Name of the employee                                                               |
| `cod_orgao`       | Code of the agency / department                                                    |
| `orgao`           | Name of the agency                                                                 |
| `tipo_empresa`    | Type of organization (e.g., direct administration, autarchy)                       |
| `sexo`            | Gender (M/F)                                                                       |
| `dt_nascimento`   | Date of birth                                                                      |
| `idade`           | Age                                                                                |
| `escolaridade`    | Education level                                                                    |
| `cod_cargo`       | Code of the position / job classification                                          |
| `cargo`           | Name of the position                                                               |
| `jornada`         | Work schedule / working hours                                                      |
| `regimejuridico`  | Legal regime (e.g., statutory, CLT)                                                |
| `tipo_contrato`   | Type of contract (permanent, temporary, commissioned)                              |
| `dt_exercicio`    | Date of starting in the position                                                   |
| `yr_service`      | Years of service                                                                   |
| `salario_base`    | Base salary                                                                        |
| `remuneracao`     | Remuneration (might include some allowances)                                       |
| `salario`         | Salary (could be same as `salario_base` or adjusted)                               |
| `beneficio`       | Benefits (monetary)                                                                |
| `bruto`           | Gross salary (before deductions)                                                   |
| `liquido`         | Net salary (after deductions)                                                      |
| `vale_transporte` | Transportation voucher                                                             |
| `sal_familia`     | Family salary allowance                                                            |
| `horas_extras`    | Overtime hours                                                                     |
| `classe`          | Job class (grade / pay band)                                                       |
| `referencia`      | Reference code (could be pay step)                                                 |
| `nivel`           | Level within the class                                                             |
| `abono_perman`    | Permanence allowance (for those who could retire but stay)                         |
| `adc_qualific`    | Qualification allowance (education bonus)                                          |
| `adc_noturno`     | Night work allowance                                                               |
| `adc_tmp_serv`    | Length-of-service bonus                                                            |
| `aux_aliment`     | Food allowance                                                                     |
| `cet_pgce`        | Specific allowance (e.g., PGCE incentive)                                          |
| `grat_inc_espec`  | Specific additional bonus (gratificação)                                           |
| `grat_cnd_esp`    | Special conditions allowance                                                       |
| `grat_func`       | Functional bonus                                                                   |
| `he_especial`     | Special overtime allowance                                                         |
| `rest_fal_abn`    | Possibly reimbursement for absence (uncertain)                                     |
| `ret_ex_aerea`    | Reimbursement / retention of aerial (flight) expenses                              |
| `ret_ex_l_pro`    | Reimbursement / retention (pro labor)                                              |
| `ret_pecuni`      | Pecuniary reimbursement / allowance                                                |
| `ret_t_at_esp`    | Reimbursement of special activities                                                |
| `risco_vida`      | Life-risk allowance                                                                |
| `subsidio`        | Subsidy (e.g., high-level fixed salary)                                            |
| `vant_pessoal`    | Personal advantage (grandfathered allowance)                                       |
| `vencimento`      | Base remuneration                                                                  |
| `fg_atece_mag`    | Specific functional bonus (e.g., for teachers)                                     |
| `g_c_e_tr_mag`    | Another special allowance related to teaching                                      |
| `gr_ex_u_e_t`     | Possibly special bonus / gratification (uncertain)                                 |
| `grat_atv_edu`    | Education activity bonus                                                           |
| `grat_atv_mag`    | Teaching activity bonus                                                            |
| `grat_es_prof`    | Professional performance bonus                                                     |
| `grat_p_titul`    | Title bonus (e.g., higher education)                                               |
| `he_cjest_mag`    | Special overtime for teaching staff                                                |
| `idge`            | Likely incentive bonus (uncertain)                                                 |
| `ret_t_f_co_a`    | Reimbursement / retention type A                                                   |
| `ret_t_f_co_b`    | Reimbursement / retention type B                                                   |
| `gr_com_j_op`     | Commissioned gratification (uncertain)                                             |
| `no_orgao`        | Full name of the agency                                                            |
| `no_cargo`        | Full name of the position                                                          |




| **Variable Name**                   | **Probable Meaning / Description**                                 |
| ----------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| `ANO_PAGAMENTO`                     | Year of payment (e.g., 2022)                                       |
| `MES_REFERENCIA`                    | Reference month (e.g., 1–12)                                       |
| `MATRICULA`                         | Employee registration number                                       |
| `CPF`                               | CPF (taxpayer ID)                                                  |
| `DATA_NASCIMENTO`                   | Date of birth                                                      |
| `GENERO`                            | Gender (M/F)                                                       |
| `ESCOLARIDADE`                      | Education level                                                    |
| `DATA_ADMISSAO`                     | Date of hiring / admission                                         |
| `ADMINISTRACAO`                     | Type of administration (e.g., direct, indirect, foundation)        |
| `TIPO_CONTRATO`                     | Type of contract (e.g., permanent, temporary, commissioned)        |
| `GRUPO`                             | Group (could be a functional or career group)                      |
| `COD_ORGAO`                         | Organization code                                                  |
| `ORGAO`                             | Organization name                                                  |
| `CARREIRA`                          | Career (broad classification of occupation)                        |
| `CARGO`                             | Position (specific job title)                                      |
| `JORNADA`                           | Work schedule (hours per week)                                     |
| `CLASSE`                            | Class (pay grade)                                                  |
| `NIVEL`                             | Level within the class                                             |
| `DATA_ULT_PROGRESSAO`               | Date of last career progression / promotion                        |
| `SALARIO_BASE`                      | Base salary                                                        |
| `CONTRIBUICAO_PREVIDENCIA`          | Social security contribution withheld                              |
| `ADICIONAL_TEMPO_SERVICO`           | Length-of-service bonus                                            |
| `COMISSAO`                          | Commission or position of trust allowance                          |
| `ABONO_PERMANENCIA`                 | Permanence bonus (when eligible for retirement but staying active) |
| `DECISAO_JUDICIAL`                  | Judicial decision payments (court-ordered)                         |
| `DEMAIS_GRATIFICACOES_TRANSITORIAS` | Other temporary bonuses / gratifications                           |
| `DEMAIS_GRATIFICACOES_CARREIRA`     | Other career-related bonuses / gratifications                      |
| `SALARIO_BRUTO`                     | Gross salary (before deductions)                                   |
| `SALARIO_LIQUIDO`                   | Net salary (after deductions)                                      |
























